{"tid":1317520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3月27號林鄭拒與王志民握手","createTime":"2019-07-14T19:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T12:28:32.000Z","uid":207792,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a29831275da070918fd5e1bba58ccae79734772d","tid":1317520,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:09:25.000Z","msg":"林鄭同中聯辦會唔會一早不和 所以依家大權唔係林鄭手中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係中聯辦同警隊到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vGeb98G4JrQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvGeb98G4JrQ&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=1b863495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vGeb98G4JrQ</a><br />\n<br />\n7月2凌晨4點係<span style=\"color: red;\">警總</span>開記招之後警隊對市民態度180度轉變 （唔排除係g20完左既關係）<br />\n<br />\n有巴打指出盧偉聰冇理由坐主席位 係都比李家超坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好有可能中聯辦已經拎左警隊控制權 架空林鄭 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭同中聯辦會唔會一早不和 所以依家大權唔係林鄭手中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而係中聯辦同警隊到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cf86HR8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCf86HR8.png&h=eef6cca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復屯公 上水先揾藍絲揾搞事 之後再用黎做藉口清場 都係689年代既手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8b99e58a87269ef4a486eee9ce0c7a9d4e599a","tid":1317520,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:14:34.000Z","msg":"大機會<br />\n尤其諗到木奠請辭被拒就覺得越似田<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958e8b5f7822044bdf4e2da6cae0c56cc97695e8","tid":1317520,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T19:18:59.000Z","msg":"早幾日成報話中聯辦出手做野 之後就有藍絲係連儂牆打人 縱火 開始引一派人打一派人 令示威者唔記得真正既焦點係政府到"},{"pid":"a0e7676cf2c221a9a0bf523ed80ea3f1a3a18543","tid":1317520,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de8b99e58a87269ef4a486eee9ce0c7a9d